creator: ZFApps
descriptionHtml:
Datalogging application for Toyota OBD1 cars.
works with the TOYOCOM & OBD1READ tools from zf-scantools.
https://zf-scantools.com/

-displays data in separate cells or all together in a graph cells
-allows to configure each cell display mode by horizontal & vertical swiping
-trip computer.
-thermal audio alarm in case your engine overheats.
-instant MPG calculator.
-Allow you to see all data received from the car through the obd1 protocol & possibly more.
-Allow to save every frame received in a database in the phone and export to *.CSV file as needed.

*********** Engines supported by TOYOBD1 **************
please visit www.zf-scantools.com to see the up to date support
